<b>But look at the proof.</b>

24
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:44,966
<b>Or actually the lack of it.</b>

25
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:46,099
<b>Take Mosul.</b>

26
00:00:47,133 --> 00:00:50,066
<b>Oil-rich, strategic, absolutely crucial.</b>

27
00:00:50,966 --> 00:00:52,766
<b>Sykes-Picot put it in the French zone.</b>

28
00:00:53,066 --> 00:00:54,566
<b>But it ended up in British Iraq.</b>

29
00:00:55,066 --> 00:00:55,966
<b>10 years later.</b>

30
00:00:56,133 --> 00:00:58,833
<b>After years of negotiations, oil company</b>

31
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:01,300
<b>deals and League of Nations Commission,</b>

32
00:01:01,966 --> 00:01:05,033
<b>Iraq's borders finalized in 1926.</b>

33
