<b>Britain gets southern Iraq.</b>

96
00:03:30,033 --> 00:03:31,599
<b>Area A, French influence.</b>

97
00:03:32,333 --> 00:03:33,933
<b>Area B, British influence.</b>

98
00:03:34,766 --> 00:03:37,566
<b>And the brown zone, Palestine, under</b>

99
00:03:37,566 --> 00:03:38,933
<b>international administration.</b>

100
00:03:39,633 --> 00:03:41,400
<b>The exact same lands they</b>

