125
00:04:42,366 --> 00:04:44,333
<b>Same Palestine, same land.</b>

126
00:04:45,133 --> 00:04:46,466
<b>That's promise number three.</b>

127
00:04:46,933 --> 00:04:49,233
<b>Three promises, two years,</b>

